data.description: Impeccably Maintained Home in Sought After Briar Chapel. 2.5 Story home with Open Kitchen Fam Rm. 3 Bed & 3.5 Bath, Has a 4th bedroom on third(no closet)  Stainless Appliances, Gas Range, Microwave, Granite Counters, White Custom Cabinetry, Farm Sink, Center Island, Plantation Shutters, Hardwoods, Fireplace, & Bookshelves on the Main Level. Spacious Primary Bedroom on 2nd w/ WIC, Dual Vanity, Garden Tub and Sep Shower, Some Hardwoods and Covered Porch. Third Floor Could be Bonus Room/4th bedroom/Home Office w/ a Full Bath which makes for a great flex space. Walk in Attic Storage too. Fenced in Backyard and 2 Car Detached Garage
